{"questionId":"14232","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Consider the vectors&nbsp;<em><strong>a</strong></em> =&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  0 \\\\   3 \\\\   p  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mi>p</mi>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> and <em><strong>b</strong></em> = <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  0 \\\\   6 \\\\   {18}  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>18</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p>\n<p>Find the value of <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"p\">\n  <mi>p</mi>\n</math></span> for which <em><strong>a</strong></em> and <em><strong>b</strong></em> are</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>perpendicular.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>evidence of scalar product<em>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em>eg &nbsp; &nbsp;</em><em><strong>a</strong></em>•<em><strong>b</strong></em>,&nbsp; (0)(0) + (3)(6) + <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" al